metadata that identifies the origin or ownership of the Project.

"Restricted Modification" means any change to the Project made by any method,
including manual editing, AI-assisted editing, automated refactoring, scripts,
codemods, batch replacement, build-time rewriting, generated patches, binary
patching, metadata editing, asset replacement, or any other direct or indirect
alteration.

"Authorized Maintainer" means DamonZS, the repository owner, a person or entity
listed in MAINTAINERS.md or granted direct write/admin permission by the
repository owner, or any human, AI assistant, script, automation, CI job, build
tool, formatting tool, or agent acting under their instruction for this Project.

